  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raccoon Roller is a physics based precision platformer that tests your creative thinking and mechanical skill. With 40 unique levels to explore, discover various routes as you race for gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.poster.avif?t=1733148580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.webm?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.mp4?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock stylish accessories and high-skill bonus levels through in-game collectables and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.poster.avif?t=1733148580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.webm?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.mp4?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master advanced movement techniques to speed through levels and become unbeatable on the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/7a42a7b5bccaa4a50cdea858bbc41482.poster.avif?t=1733148580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/7a42a7b5bccaa4a50cdea858bbc41482.webm?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/7a42a7b5bccaa4a50cdea858bbc41482.mp4?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADDITIONAL FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard support with optional friends filtering.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/b4374f6e33ac970c060111bb57ef99f6.avif?t=1733148580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras_big/b4374f6e33ac970c060111bb57ef99f6.avif?t=1733148580 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raccoon Roller is a physics based precision platformer that tests your creative thinking and mechanical skill. With 40 unique levels to explore, discover various routes as you race for gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.poster.avif?t=1733148580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.webm?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/671530b2991c632479e4b7d44c23f8db.mp4?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock stylish accessories and high-skill bonus levels through in-game collectables and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.poster.avif?t=1733148580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.webm?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373980/extras/03099b370fb24b3cf676d0eb9ce55aab.mp4?t=1733148580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master advanced movement techniques to speed through levels and become unbeatable on the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared